nter wp-image-4815 size-full jetpack-lazy-image jetpack-lazy-image--handled\" src=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\" srcset=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4.jpg 670w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4-272x272.jpg 272w\" alt=\"\" width=\"670\" height=\"670\" data-attachment-id=\"4815\" data-permalink=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-cho-tung-khong-gian-trong-nha-ban/interior-design-of-a-modern-living-room/\" data-orig-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"670,670\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 400D DIGITAL&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Interior design of a modern living room.&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1158845511&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;15&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;400&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.076923076923077&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Interior design of a modern living room.&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Interior design of a modern living room.\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-4.jpg\" data-lazy-loaded=\"1\" /></a>\n\nĐối với những gia đình có trẻ em, phòng ngủ của các bé nên chọn những loại giấy dán tường có màu sắc vui tươi, sống động để kích thích trí tưởng tượng của các bé. Với các bé gái có thể chọn các gam màu hồng, vàng…với các hình công chúa hoặc hoa lá tươi tắn. Còn với các bé trai là các màu mạnh mẽ hơn như xanh dương, xanh lá…với các hình ảnh như: ô tô, máy bay, siêu nhân hoặc những nhân vật hoạt hình mà bé yêu thích…\n\n<a class=\"no-light-gallery\" href=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1.jpeg\" data-src=\"\" data-sub-html=\"\" data-alt=\"\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4811 size-full jetpack-lazy-image jetpack-lazy-image--handled\" src=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1.jpeg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px\" srcset=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1.jpeg 1152w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1-300x211.jpeg 300w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1-768x540.jpeg 768w, https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1-1024x720.jpeg 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1152\" height=\"810\" data-attachment-id=\"4811\" data-permalink=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-cho-tung-khong-gian-trong-nha-ban/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-1.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"1152,810\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong (1)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"h